divs: Sighting Detailstaking random pictures of the clouds, hoping to catch something. It is a pretty common thing to do. I always do a complete circle from my back deck, about 8 pictures total every time. This showed up on the second batch. looks like a triangle, but if anyone can focus it into a bird or bug, please do. I also catch random discs occasionally, but they are always out of focus
